translations: v.铲除野草（weed 的过去式）

phrs.translation: 除草；杂草防除；野草控制

sentences.sentence: When he weeded out "the most doubtful measures of aggression", only 28% supported a connection.
sentences.translation: 当他排除“最可疑的攻击手段”时，只有28%的人支持这种联系。

sentences.sentence: The weaker ones were weeded out.
sentences.translation: 由此弱者被淘汰出局也在情理之中。
但它们必须要被铲除么？
